## Contribution Notes

- Mirror any logic change to both Android (Kotlin) and iOS (Swift)
- Don't add language packs without proper frequency data
- TextFixEngine: only add fixes with >99% confidence — when in doubt, don't
- All config format: TOML (not YAML)
- No force-pushes to `main`
